---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { PROCEDURE_CATALOG, PROCEDURE_PILLAR_SUMMARIES } from '../data/procedure-catalog';
---

<Layout
  title="시술 안내"
  description="에스리본 클리닉 시술 안내 — EBD·주사·경구약·외용제를 영역별로 정리했습니다."
>
  <div class="proc-page">
    <header class="proc-hero">
      <p class="proc-hero-badge">Treatments</p>
      <h1 class="proc-hero-title">시술 안내</h1>
      <p class="proc-hero-lead">
        블로그와 별도로, 클리닉에서 다루는 치료를 <strong>EBD(기기)</strong> · <strong>주사</strong> · <strong>경구약</strong> ·
        <strong>외용제</strong> 네 축으로 정리했습니다. 실제 시행·적응증은 내원 시 의료진이 판단합니다.
      </p>
    </header>

    <nav class="proc-toc" aria-label="시술 영역 바로가기">
      {PROCEDURE_PILLAR_SUMMARIES.map((p) => (
        <a href={`#${p.id}`} class="proc-toc-link">
          <span class="proc-toc-label">{p.label}</span>
          <span class="proc-toc-short">{p.short}</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </nav>

    <p class="proc-disclaimer" role="note">
      아래 목록은 <strong>의학적 정보 안내용 분류</strong>이며, 모든 항목이 본원에서 시행된다는 뜻은 아닙니다. 약물·시술은 부작용·금기가 있을 수 있으니
      반드시 진료를 통해 결정합니다.
    </p>

    {PROCEDURE_CATALOG.map((pillar) => (
      <section class="proc-pillar" id={pillar.id} aria-labelledby={`heading-${pillar.id}`}>
        <div class="proc-pillar-head">
          <h2 class="proc-pillar-title" id={`heading-${pillar.id}`}>
            {pillar.title}
          </h2>
          <p class="proc-pillar-sub">{pillar.subtitle}</p>
          <p class="proc-pillar-intro">{pillar.intro}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="proc-subgrid">
          {pillar.subgroups.map((sub) => (
            <article class="proc-subcard">
              <h3 class="proc-subtitle">{sub.title}</h3>
              <ul class="proc-item-list">
                {sub.items.map((item) => (
                  <li>
                    <span class="proc-item-name">{item.name}</span>
                    {item.note && <span class="proc-item-note">{item.note}</span>}
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>
    ))}

    <footer class="proc-footer">
      <p>
        시술·약에 대한 <strong>심화 글·FAQ</strong>는 <a href="/blog">블로그</a>에서 확인하실 수 있습니다.
      </p>
      <p>
        위치·연락은 <a href="/about#location">오시는 길</a>, 문의는 <a href="/consult">온라인 상담</a>을 이용해 주세요.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .proc-page {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 3.5rem;
    word-break: keep-all;
  }

  .proc-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .proc-hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.3);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .proc-hero-title {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-hero-lead {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 40rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-hero-lead strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .proc-toc {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .proc-toc-link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 14px);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .proc-toc-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .proc-toc-label {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-toc-short {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--t3);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .proc-disclaimer {
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 14px);
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-pillar {
    scroll-margin-top: 5.5rem;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .proc-pillar:first-of-type {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .proc-pillar-head {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .proc-pillar-title {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-pillar-sub {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  .proc-pillar-intro {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--t2);
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .proc-subgrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .proc-subcard {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 22px);
    padding: 1.15rem 1.2rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  .proc-subtitle {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .proc-item-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.55rem;
  }

  .proc-item-list li {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--t2);
    padding-left: 0.65rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-gold-light);
  }

  .proc-item-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-item-note {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--t3);
  }

  .proc-footer {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-footer a {
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.15em;
  }

  .proc-footer p {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .proc-footer p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .proc-toc {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
